BOOK TICKETS TO THE ULTIMATE JAZZ PARTY IN COPENHAGEN: rsvp-popup.com/events/the-ultimate-jazz-party-soelyst-2017

Grammy winner Randy Brecker in this moving clip about his friend - another legend & 6 time grammy nominee Mike Stern - who broke both his shoulders, but now is ready to rock the stage at The Ultimate Jazz Party 2017 in Copenhagen July 8th & 9th.
